data.text:
Band Of Brothers 8

With the war winding down, Easy Company moves into an Alsatian town near the German border. Still on the frontline, the men sleep just across the river from the Nazis.

The L.A.

When Summer and Marissa receive invitations for famous actor Grady Bridges' birthday party in LA, the girls decide to take Ryan and Seth along with them to join in the fun.

Godzilla and a Sprig of Mint

Christy's night takes an unexpected turn when she meets her attractive neighbour, while Alvin's ex-wife interrupts his plans with Bonnie.

Whiskey Tango Foxtrot

After a bombing at a party that kills the Secretary of the Navy, DOD inspector Parsons starts to believe Gibbs and helps him find the people trying to kill the NCIS team.
